  "texts": [
    "In such cases, instead of specifying all sets of instructions, researchers can describe why specific sets of instructions are not added.",
    "We want to emphasize that any reason can be valid, also depending on one's perspective: we propose DCTs as a tool for increasing transparency, not to enforce a given normative perspective (except perhaps the open science imperative to optimize transparency).",
